node.text: From reefs to ridges, explore the beauty of the Philippines through the eyes of the locals. While 2020 has been a year of change for travel, the Philippines is excited to invite local visitors to explore the beautiful islands. The #BDTeam had the pleasure of working with @tourism_phl to highlight beautiful places around the Philippines. The opportunities for exploration are endless-from the Hundred Island National Park in Pangasinan to exploring the Suba and Culili Sand Dunes in Ilocos Norte.

With an incredibly rich history, being an “Egyptian” can have many facets especially when it comes to creativity. Today, we’re sharing a unique story dedicated to any creative who intends to carve their own path no matter the circumstances. 

“It’s proof that the end product most of the time doesn’t pan out the way you expect it. And its by having expectations that you hinder your potential.” - @matiasderada

Watch this beautiful film on Beautiful Destinations Youtube channel. 🇪🇬

🎥 @matiasderada #BDTeam

Bristol Bay, one of Alaska’s most treasured natural wonders, is under threat. @world_wildlife 

It’s home to an irreplaceable ecosystem and one of the last salmon strongholds. Not only that, its iconic wildlife has sprung up a sustainable tourism industry which effects thousands of Alaskan livelihoods.

All of this is under threat if the Pebble Mine moves forward. The recent approval of the environmental impact statement has made it clear that our voices need to be heard. 

Nature and people can’t live without fresh water, and Bristol Bay is the lifeblood that sustains every species calling the region home. 

On a recent trip to Alaska, the #BDTeam and WWF Ambassador, @jeremyjauncey, learned firsthand about the conservation community’s fight against Pebble Mine.

node.text: As New York City starts to open back up, we wanted to take a moment to reflect on the efforts of heroes in the hospitality industry who have been helping our frontline workers. @fsnewyork was the first hotel in New York City to open its door to our frontline workers and provide them with a safe haven to stay during such an uncertain time. They quickly transformed the hotel into a near medical-grade facility. Over 300 medical workers called @fsnewyork home during this time as they were provided rooms free of charge. This allowed them to keep their own families safe as they focused on their work and taking care of patients. ❤️ (🎥: @loganlambert 📸: @loganstrongarms 📍: Four Seasons Hotel New York)

Basking with @florina__toma via @adrianbaias in this beautiful corner of Ios, Greece. ☀️ With breathtaking views of Papas Beach, this cozy shaded corner furnished with a hanging bed can't get any dreamier. ☁️

What have you heard about Ios and what are your favorite islands in Greece? 🇬🇷

📽 @florina__toma & @adrianbaias 
📍 Ios, Greece

Aboard an idyllic ride via @swiss, which paves the way to views of green pastures, pristine lakes, and charming villages. If you enjoy scenic train rides, you'll absolutely delight in exploring Switzerland.🇨🇭

The Lucerne–Interlaken Express is a two-hour ride that will take you past invigorating lakes, breathtaking waterfalls, and over the majestic Brünig mountain pass. Throughout the ride, you'll bask in utmost comfort while gazing outside its large panoramic windows. 🚂

What's the most scenic train ride you've experienced? 🍃

📽 @swiss
📍 Lungern, Switzerland
🎶 Billie Eilish, Khalid - lovely

Morocco blues via @delafuentecam. 💙 Tucked in northern Morocco, Chefchaouen is nicknamed the "blue pearl of Morocco" because its homes and shops are painted with different shades of blue. 

A magical place to get lost in, tourists head to this city for recreation and relaxation. Get lost in the maze of streets, go shopping at one of the many little bazaars, and learn about the place's history at the Kasbah Museum.

Have you been to this fabulous city? What are the best places to go to in Morocco for first-time travelers there? 🇲🇦

📸 @delafuentecam
📍 Chefchaouen, Morocco

Filmmaker @elliotgrafton had the honor of setting out on a 4-day expedition in South Australia's Neptune Islands to capture footage of great whites onboard @rodneyfoxsharkedxpeditions! 🛥️

"They're not crazy man-eaters but are beautiful creatures in our ocean that we should protect and look after." 🦈 Despite encountering an attack by a great white shark in 1963, Rodney Fox didn't stop exploring the oceans. Instead of letting fear paralyze him, he let his fascination push him forward, going so far as to building the first-ever underwater shark observation cage and pioneering shark cage diving.

Check the link in our bio to watch the film Elliot created to tell the story of Rodney Fox! 🎬 

Would you also like to try cage diving with great white sharks?

📽 @elliotgrafton 
📍 Neptune Islands, South Australia

The most perfect day with @amedved.film, with views as excellent as the weather. 🌞🍃 This was shot in the Altai Mountains, a mountain range that spans Russia, Mongolia, Kazakhstan, and a small part of China. The area offers a variety of landscapes that make it perfect for all kinds of outdoor sports, such as trekking, backpacking, skateboarding, climbing, kayaking, and mountaineering. 🇷🇺

When was the last time you spent a day outdoors? Tag your skate crew and adventure buddies! 🛹

📽 @amedved.film
📍 Altai Mountains
🎶 AURORA - Runaway

🚶‍♂️ @jacobjetski 
📽 @nicksurfnick 
📍 Bahia, Brazil

Magical moments aboard @lakecomo_boat. 🛶 A respite for those seeking calm, Nesso is a tranquil village sitting on the banks of Lake Como in Italy. 🇮🇹

The Nesso Gorge, locally known as Orrido di Nesso, is one of the best natural wonders in Lake Como. You can enjoy the views on the Ponte della Civera, a Romanesque bridge made of stone, or by going on an idyllic boat tour. 

What's been the most memorable boat ride in your travels, and would you love to experience this? ❤️

📽 @lakecomo_boat 
📍 Nesso Gorge, Italy
🎶 Kina - Get You The Moon

In the woods with @shabil_panchili, @nijaz_manali, and a furry friend in the beautiful Himalayan resort of Manali in India. 🦮🌳

A majestic enclave known for its cool climate, snow-capped mountains, and rich cultural heritage, Manali is a sought-after destination that has something for everybody. Whether you're after a solo trip, a fun escape with friends, a family holiday, or a romantic vacation, you'll be pleased to find both adventure and relaxation here. 😍

Have you been to Manali and would you love to explore this destination? 🇮🇳

📽 @shabil_panchili & @nijaz_manali 
📍 Manali, Himachal Pradesh, India
